  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of our study to quantitatively examine the stress levels prior to surgery and the
      use of analgesics post surgery in both children and their parents following a preoperative
      intervention with a medical clown compared to children that were not exposed to this
      intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
